<L>__{exterior building day}
<A>__{on a street hector stands with a policeman watching mrs. philippopolis being loaded into the ambulance. her son is with her. when she is safely inside he walks towards hector. fortunately he is of modest build, and a head shorter than hector, and he seems to be saving his wrath for the courthouse.}
